snippet.title: Best VGM 2102 - Castlevania : Aria of Sorrow - Inner Quarters
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1152 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FJJPaBA7264
Best VGN 1609 - http://youtu.be/2ZX41kMN9V8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GBA
Castlevania : Aria of Sorrow (2003)
Inner Quarters / Phantom Palace Fountain
Michiru Yamane
